            <h1>When is it a problem?</h1>

            <p>Violence is not love. <br><br>
                Love means caring, supporting, understanding and respecting each other. <br><br>
                Violence means disrespect, mercilessness and possession; it starts with jealousy, cruelty and ends with revenge.  <br></p>

